  "reference_number": "RUS3474",
  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that KUNPENG (IMO 9247194) is, has been, or is likely to be involved in an activity whose object or effect is to destabilise Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. Namely, KUNPENG is, has been or is likely to be involved in carrying a good from a place in Russia to a third country that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n",
